articles.title: PUNCH LINE (German Dub) - Episode 5 - Ito Dies
articles.description: Yuta witnesses the worst-case scenario as was warned in the video.

articles.title: PUNCH LINE (German Dub) - Episode 3 - Martians Attack!
articles.description: Ito is beginning to suspect who Mikatan really is. Mikatan tries desperately to hide the truth. Meanwhile, a mysterious man, Miyazawa Kenji, invades, and Meika's true identity is also revealed.

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 4 - What Comes Suddenly and Never Leaves?
articles.description: It's three straight days of testing for Class Black. While Haru is intent on passing those tests, another one of the girls is intent on killing her.

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 13
PUNCH LINE (German Dub) - Episode 9 - Brazilian High Kick
articles.description: Concerned about Mikatan's health, Yuta tells her to stop her hero activities, but she refuses to listen. He talks to Meika to have her run physical exams.

articles.title: PUNCH LINE (German Dub) - Episode 10 - The Fall
articles.description: The Human Salvation Project ends in failure, leaving Yuta in despair. Ito is abducted, and Yuta and Mikatan search for her at the shrine, where they learn the truth about everything that's happened.

articles.title: PUNCH LINE (German Dub) - Episode 7 - Panty Panic Returns
articles.description: The panty panic is back! Now, everyone together! "Panty Panic! Panty Panic!" Many things are revealed, including the relationship between Yuta seeing panties and the end of the world.

articles.title: PUNCH LINE (German Dub) - Episode 2 - The Lace of Compassion
articles.description: Having failed in her requested exorcism, Rabura is feeling down. Meika has an idea to cheer her up. Meanwhile, a strange scream comes from hermit Ito's room.

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 11 - How to Tell Apart a 'Felicitation' From a 'Curse'
articles.description: The truth about Class Black is revealed, and Tokaku and Haru must grapple with the implications of this new information.

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 8 - Which Gatekeeper Is the One Who Lies?
articles.description: The field has been whittled to four assassins. With classes done and a typhoon closing in, Haru and Tokaku are in for a harrowing evening.

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 3 - What's Red, But Isn't Red?
articles.description: Tokaku switches sides to Haru, but the game is still on and the first official Class Black assassination attempt is made.

articles.title: PUNCH LINE (German Dub) - Episode 1 - Panty Panic
articles.description: An incident causes Yutaro's soul to leave his body. As he searches Koraikan for a way home, he catches a glimpse of the female tenants' panties, leading to unspeakable disaster on earth! Why?!

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 9 - What Dwells In Your Heart? (Make-up Test)
articles.description: Tokaku faces Isuke and her own inner demons, while Haru desperately tries to stay ahead of Shinya.

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 1 - The World is Full of ___
articles.description: Thirteen students in all in Year 10, Class Black. Twelve assassins, one target. The first to kill the target will get whatever they want. As one of the assasins, Tokaku Azuma joins Class Black and begins to size up the competition.

articles.title: PUNCH LINE (German Dub) - Episode 11 - Secret Squad Justice Punch!
articles.description: Yuta pleads for Meika's help in saving humanity from destruction. The two begin "Operation Peacemaker," but to make it work, Yuta must defend Koraikan by himself.

articles.title: PUNCH LINE (German Dub) - Episode 6 - It's New Year's Eve, Meikaemon
articles.description: Yuta brings an end to the video crimes, but the countdown to the end of humanity had already begun.

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 5 - How Do You Get A Bird Out of Its Cage?
articles.description: Class Black prepares to put on a production of "Romeo and Juliet" for the school festival and another assassin tries her luck.

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 2 - What Dwells In Your Heart?
articles.description: All 13 students are now assembled and things are about to get serious. But one of them thinks she can jump the gun and beat everyone to the prize.

articles.title: PUNCH LINE (German Dub) - Episode 4 - Possessed by the Stripes
articles.description: Having seen an ominous video, Yuta learns that Ito is in danger. He tries to let everyone know by possessing Rabura, when Gliese, the man she has feelings for, shows up.

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 12 - Therefore, the World is Full of ___
articles.description: Now that Tokaku has delivered her advance notice, the three remaining members of Class Black have one last assassination attempt to sort out.

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 10 - Who Is the Queen?
articles.description: With Class Black down to four students, Tokaku and Haru face off against the person they consider to be their final opponent.

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 6 - Every Pretty Flower Has Its ___
articles.description: Class Black puts on "Romeo and Juliet" in front of a student audience, but with so many deaths in the play, maybe one or two will be real.

articles.title: Riddle Story of Devil (German Dub) - Episode 7 - What Can You Never Outrun?
articles.description: Another assassin tries her hand, but this one proposes a game with rules that will give Haru and Tokaku a chance to beat her fair and square.

articles.title: PUNCH LINE (German Dub) - Episode 12 - Punch Line
articles.description: What is the fate of humanity? Will humanity come to a supremely happy and peaceful future? What's the punch line?
